ANC treasurer-general Paul Mashatile opened the ANC Limpopo conference on Friday. Mashatile received a warm welcome from delegates as he made his way to the podium to begin addressing them. They welcomed him in song, “phakama Mashatile, ixesha lifikile” (rise up Mashatile, the time is now). TimesLIVE Support independent journalism by subscribing to the Sunday Times. Just R20 for the first month.